{
  "source_id": "sage",
  "entity_id": "sage-intacct-arinvoice",
  "mapping_version": "v1",
  "_comment": [
    "Canonical mapping for Sage Intacct accounts-receivable/invoice object.",
    "",
    "AR invoices are transactional records — one row per invoice issued to a",
    "customer.  The Intacct REST API returns these as a collection under the",
    "accounts-receivable/invoice endpoint with incremental extraction on",
    "auditInfo.modifiedAt.",
    "",
    "PK: 'id' (Intacct invoice record number) → 'invoice_id'.",
    "  This is the system-assigned numeric identifier; it uniquely identifies",
    "  an invoice within a given Intacct company.  No cross-source deduplication",
    "  is performed — Intacct is the sole source of truth for AR invoices.",
    "",
    "Financial totals: Intacct returns monetary amounts as strings in the REST",
    "  API.  All amount fields are cast to decimal for downstream analytics.",
    "",
    "State values: 'Draft', 'Pending', 'Posted', 'Paid', 'Reversed', 'Voided'.",
    "  Mapped as a raw string to 'invoice_status'.",
    "",
    "Customer FK: 'customerId' is the Intacct customer code that joins to the",
    "  'account_id' field in the sage-intacct-customer curated dataset."
  ],
  "rules": [
    {
      "source_fields": ["id"],
      "canonical_field": "invoice_id",
      "transformation": "rename",
      "transformation_params": {},
      "missing_field_behavior": "raise_error"
    },
    {
      "source_fields": ["customerId"],
      "canonical_field": "customer_id",
      "transformation": "rename",
      "transformation_params": {},
      "missing_field_behavior": "raise_error"
    },
    {
      "source_fields": ["state"],
      "canonical_field": "invoice_status",
      "transformation": "rename",
      "transformation_params": {},
      "missing_field_behavior": "drop_field"
    },
    {
      "source_fields": ["currency"],
      "canonical_field": "currency_code",
      "transformation": "rename",
      "transformation_params": {},
      "missing_field_behavior": "drop_field"
    },
    {
      "source_fields": ["totalEntered"],
      "canonical_field": "invoice_amount",
      "transformation": "cast",
      "transformation_params": { "type": "decimal" },
      "missing_field_behavior": "use_default",
      "default_value": "0"
    },
    {
      "source_fields": ["totalPaid"],
      "canonical_field": "amount_paid",
      "transformation": "cast",
      "transformation_params": { "type": "decimal" },
      "missing_field_behavior": "use_default",
      "default_value": "0"
    },
    {
      "source_fields": ["totalDue"],
      "canonical_field": "amount_due",
      "transformation": "cast",
      "transformation_params": { "type": "decimal" },
      "missing_field_behavior": "use_default",
      "default_value": "0"
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Invoice date — the date the invoice was issued.",
      "source_fields": ["invoiceDate"],
      "canonical_field": "invoice_date",
      "transformation": "date_format",
      "transformation_params": {
        "input_format": "%Y-%m-%d",
        "output_format": "%Y-%m-%d"
      },
      "missing_field_behavior": "drop_field"
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Payment due date — used for aging calculations.",
      "source_fields": ["dueDate"],
      "canonical_field": "due_date",
      "transformation": "date_format",
      "transformation_params": {
        "input_format": "%Y-%m-%d",
        "output_format": "%Y-%m-%d"
      },
      "missing_field_behavior": "drop_field"
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Intacct REST API returns timestamps in ISO-8601 UTC: 2024-01-15T10:30:00Z",
      "source_fields": ["auditInfo.createdAt"],
      "canonical_field": "created_date",
      "transformation": "date_format",
      "transformation_params": {
        "input_format": "%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ",
        "output_format": "%Y-%m-%d"
      },
      "missing_field_behavior": "drop_field"
    },
    {
      "source_fields": ["auditInfo.modifiedAt"],
      "canonical_field": "last_modified_date",
      "transformation": "date_format",
      "transformation_params": {
        "input_format": "%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ",
        "output_format": "%Y-%m-%d"
      },
      "missing_field_behavior": "drop_field"
    }
  ]
}
